					<p>Identifying blind spots isn't about paranoia‚Äîit's about pragmatism. Leading research institutions understand that you can maintain an open, collaborative environment while implementing smart security measures. The key is finding the right balance: <strong>as open as possible, but as secure as necessary</strong>.</p>

					<p>Here's how organizations are transforming their approach:</p>

					<div class="solution-list">
						<div class="solution-item">
